2021-05-22 Camille Coti <camille.coti [aatt] lipn.univ-paris13 [ddoott] fr>

	* added measurement functions for OpenSHMEM

	* added a configuration and compilation system using the Autotools

	* added OpenSHMEM support in the infrastructure, making it
	possible to use using OpenSHMEM environments that do not also
	support MPI.

